response.overview: STEREOPHONICS You Gotta Go There To Come Back - Fanclub DVD Collection (Rare DVD box set collection for the album, which comprises of 3 DVD singles and also an Introduction Disc [exclusive to this box] set inside a multi foldout box sleeve, only available from the Fanclub. A nice collectors item featuring Madame Helga, Maybe Tomorrow and Since I Told You It's Over).
